name: Quilted Collage 04 - Cape of Good Hope
description:
This 1000x1000 generative image was created in Processing using an image quilting algorithm that samples one or more images and attempts to quilt the samples together in a manner that produces another coherent image. 

Tweaking the algorithm changes the size of the samples and the error tolerance associated with the quilting, producing a variety of different visual effects. 

The photographs from which this image was generated were taken by the artist at the Cape of Good Hope in South Africa.
